The paper uses bibliometric methods to analyze the relationship between the engineering and physical sciences and the health and life sciences. It combines two different approaches, one based on term map visualizations and the other on citation-based network analysis. The paper does not focus on a specific area of computer science, but it does use computational methods and techniques. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.DL (Digital Libraries), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
